parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gas Tank Stress Crack and Fuel Leak
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stress crack in the gas tank can cause fuel to leak, which can lead to a fire hazard, especially if the fuel comes into contact with the exhaust system, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Fuel leak from the gas tank
hairline crack on the upper right mount area of the tank
fuel running out of the tank.
